            <h2>The Great Exhibition <br> &ndash; an art project by local primary school children</h2>

            <p>Pupils from local schools, Rockmount, Cypress, Malcolm and All Saints, will be submitting their best
                artwork for The Great Exhibition (<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/97280290@N07/sets/72157634054191739/">See the entries on Flickr</a>.
                10 shortlisted pieces will be exhibited in shop windows during the festival. The winning piece will be
                professionally framed as a prize. Participating traders are:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><a href="http://www.acorn.ltd.uk/">Acorn Residential Sales and Lettings</a>, 29 Westow St (the winner)</li>
                <li><a href="http://www.bluedoorbicycles.com/">Blue Door Bicycles</a>, 5 and 7 Central Hill</li>
                <li><a href="http://www.winkball.com/entries/yigR6FEiMwTp/">Top Quality Dry Cleaners</a>, 9 Westow Hill</li>
                <li>Top Quality Shoe Repairs and Key Cutting, 38 Westow Hill</li>
                <li><a href="http://www.crystaleyecentre.com/">Opticians Crystal Eye Centre</a>, 20 Westow Hill</li>
                <li><a href="http://www.planta.co.uk/">Planta</a>, 32 Westow Hill</li>
                <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/papagaiotoys">Papa Gaio</a>, 83 Church Road.</li>
            </ul>

